ation\n\n```bash\nnpm install @node-minify/core @node-minify/uglify-js\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```js\nimport { minify } from '@node-minify/core';\nimport { uglifyJs } from '@node-minify/uglify-js';\n\nawait minify({\n  compressor: uglifyJs,\n  input: 'foo.js',\n  output: 'bar.js'\n});\n```\n\n## Documentation\n\nVisit https://node-minify.2clics.net for full documentation\n\n## License\n\n[MIT](https://github.com/srod/node-minify/blob/main/LICENSE)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}